| Characteristic | One-Time | Occasional | Regular | Active | Power User |
|----------------|----------|------------|---------|--------|------------|
| Mean Words | {% for s in ['one_time', 'occasional', 'regular', 'active', 'power_user'] %}{% if chars[s] %}{{ chars[s].get('mean_words', 0) | num(0) }}{% else %}—{% endif %}{% if not loop.last %} | {% endif %}{% endfor %} |
| Mean Pages | {% for s in ['one_time', 'occasional', 'regular', 'active', 'power_user'] %}{% if chars[s] %}{{ chars[s].get('mean_pages', 0) | num(1) }}{% else %}—{% endif %}{% if not loop.last %} | {% endif %}{% endfor %} |
